'''Bredisker''' was a thief of the 12th century [[DR]]. 

In the [[1177 DR|Year of the Majesty, 1177 DR]], in the southern [[Sword Coast]] lands, Bredisker successfully stole the ''[[Tome of Torment]]'', the holiest book of the faith of [[Ilmater]] the Crying God. Bredisker fled east to the [[Thornwood]], but was continually harassed and stalked by the Ilmatari. A weary Bredisker soon sold the book to [[Lalaskra]] of [[Ormpetarr]], a priestess of [[Loviatar]] and an enemy of the church.
